## 2. Files added or modified by this project

### 2.1 New files (added by DiffIML authors)

| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `IMDLBenCo/model_zoo/diffiml/diffiml.py` | `DiffIML`, `LightVAE`, `SlimVAE`, `VAE`, `ConditionEncoder`, `Unet` modules |
| `IMDLBenCo/model_zoo/diffiml/segformer.py` | Segformer (mit-b2 / b3 / b4 / b5) backbone adapted for use as the condition encoder |
| `IMDLBenCo/model_zoo/diffiml/resnet.py` | Auxiliary backbone |
| `IMDLBenCo/training_scripts/train_light_vae.py` | Distillation / training script for the lightweight mask VAE |
| `IMDLBenCo/training_scripts/gen_robustness_image.py` | Robustness curve plotting utility |
| `IMDLBenCo/evaluation/eval_vae_upper_bound.py` | Upper-bound evaluation for the mask VAE |
| `evaluate_light_vae.py` | Pixel-space comparison between teacher VAE and LightVAE |
| `evaluate_light_vae_latent.py` | Latent-space comparison between teacher VAE and LightVAE |
| `runs/demo_train_diffiml.sh` | Stage-2 training launcher for DiffIML |
| `runs/demo_train_light_vae.sh` | Stage-1 training launcher for LightVAE |
| `runs/demo_test_diffiml.sh` | Multi-benchmark evaluation launcher |
| `runs/demo_test_robustness_diffiml.sh` | Robustness evaluation launcher |
| `runs/balanced_dataset.json` (template) | Training dataset configuration template |
| `runs/test_datasets.json` (template) | Testing dataset configuration template |
| `README.md` | Project landing page (re-written for DiffIML) |
| `requirements.txt` | Python dependency list |
| `CHANGELOG.md` | Release notes |
| `CONTRIBUTING.md` | Contribution guideline |
| `NOTICE` | This file |

### 2.2 Modified files (forked from IMDLBenCo)

| Path | Nature of modification |
|---|---|
| `IMDLBenCo/model_zoo/__init__.py` | Register the new `DiffIML` model |
| `IMDLBenCo/training_scripts/demo.py` | Demo path updated for DiffIML |
| `IMDLBenCo/training_scripts/test_robust.py` | Compatibility tweaks for DiffIML inference outputs |
| `IMDLBenCo/training_scripts/utils/misc.py` | Minor logging / DDP-related adjustments |
| `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata renamed for DiffIML |
| `MANIFEST.in` | Updated to include new top-level docs and exclude large weights |
| `.gitignore` | Extended to ignore checkpoints, large logs and personal artefacts |

All other files under `IMDLBenCo/` (e.g. `iml_vit/`, `cat_net/`,
`mvss_net/`, `trufor/`, `mantra_net/`, `object_former/`, `pscc_net/`,
`span/`, `opensdi/`, `latent_iml/`, `sdiml/`, `noise_det/`,
