## 4. Datasets

Datasets used in our experiments are released by their original authors and
must be obtained from the official sources. They are **not** redistributed
in this repository. Users are responsible for complying with the licenses
of each dataset:

* CASIA v1 / v2 — <https://github.com/namtpham/casia2groundtruth>
* Columbia — <https://www.ee.columbia.edu/ln/dvmm/downloads/AuthSplicedDataSet/>
* Coverage — <https://github.com/wenbihan/coverage>
* NIST16 — <https://www.nist.gov/itl/iad/mig/media-forensics-challenge>
* IMD2020 — <http://staff.utia.cas.cz/novozada/db/>
* tampCOCO / compRAISE — released via [CAT-Net](https://github.com/mjkwon2021/CAT-Net)
* FantasticReality — <http://zoi.utia.cas.cz/files/Fantastic_Reality.tar.gz>
* Autosplice — <https://github.com/shanface33/AutoSplice_Dataset>
* CocoGlide — released via [TruFor](https://github.com/grip-unina/TruFor)

